{
  "name": "ShadowFormat",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>Shadow</strong>属性可返回一个 <strong>ShadowFormat</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例给第一张工作表添加带阴影的矩形。半透明蓝色阴影在矩形右侧偏移 5 磅，在矩形上方偏移 3 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeRectangle, <span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">128</span>)\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = msoShadow17\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OffsetX</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OffsetY</span> = -<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Transparency</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第二个形状阴影的大小。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Size</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表形状的阴影格式。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)\n{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) \n    {\n    \t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> \n    {\n    \t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Blur",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定底纹的模糊度。可读/写 <strong>Single</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中第二个形状阴影的模糊度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Blur</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表中第一个形状阴影的模糊度设置为8。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Blur</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">8</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "ForeColor",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>ColorFormat</strong>对象，它代表指定的前景填充色或纯色。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表中第三个形状阴影的前景色设置为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表中第二个形状阴影的前景色设置为蓝色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "ColorFormat",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Obscured",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>MsoTriState</strong>可以是下列 <strong>MsoTriState</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoCTrue</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoFalse</strong>阴影没有填充；如果形状也没有填充，透过形状可看见阴影的轮廓。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTriStateToggle</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoTrue</strong>指定形状的阴影有填充并被该形状所遮蔽，即使形状也没有填充。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>如果指定形状的阴影是填充的，并且阴影被形状所遮盖（即便该形状没有填充），那么该值为 <strong>True</strong>。如果阴影没有填充，并且当形状没有填充时，可透过形状看到阴影的轮廓，那么该值为 <strong>False</strong>。<strong>MsoTriState</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中的形状 3 阴影是否被遮盖。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Obscured</span> == msoTrue)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第二个形状阴影是否被遮盖。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Obscured</span> == msoTrue)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTriState",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "OffsetX",
      "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>IncrementOffsetX</strong> 方法或 <strong>IncrementOffsetY</strong>方法可将阴影从当前位置水平或垂直轻微移动而无需指定其绝对位置。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>以磅为单位返回或设置指定形状的阴影的水平偏移量。正偏移值将阴影向右偏移，负偏移值将阴影向左偏移。可读写。<strong>Single</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为第一张工作表中的形状 3 设置阴影的格式类型、水平偏移量和垂直偏移量。阴影相对形状向右偏移 5 磅，向上偏移 3 磅。如果形状没有阴影，本示例为其添加一个阴影。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = msoShadow17\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OffsetX</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OffsetY</span> = -<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第二个形状阴影的水平偏移量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OffsetX</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "OffsetY",
      "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>IncrementOffsetX</strong> 方法或 <strong>IncrementOffsetY</strong>方法可将阴影从当前位置水平或垂直轻微移动而无需指定其绝对位置。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>以磅为单位返回或设置指定形状阴影的垂直偏移。正偏移值将阴影向下偏移，负偏移值将阴影向上偏移。可读写。<strong>Single</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为第一张工作表中的形状 3 设置阴影的格式类型、水平偏移量和垂直偏移量。阴影相对形状向右偏移 5 磅，向上偏移 3 磅。如果形状没有阴影，本示例为其添加一个阴影。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = msoShadow17\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OffsetX</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OffsetY</span> = -<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第一个形状阴影的垂直偏移量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">OffsetY</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "RotateWithShape",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>MsoTriState</strong> 类型的值，该值表示是否在旋转形状时旋转阴影。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中第二个形状是否在旋转形状时旋转阴影。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RotateWithShape</span> == msoTrue)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表中第三个形状在旋转形状时旋转阴影。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RotateWithShape</span> = msoTrue\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTriState",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Size",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定底纹的大小。可读/写 <strong>Single</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中第二个形状阴影的大小。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Size</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为活动工作表中第三个形状设置阴影类型并设置阴影大小为90。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = msoShadow16\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Size</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">90</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Style",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>MsoShadowStyle 可以是下列 <strong>MsoShadowStyle</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>msoShadowStyleInnerShadow</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoShadowStyleMixed</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>msoShadowStyleOuterShadow</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定底纹的样式。可读/写 <strong>MsoShadowStyle</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中第二个形状阴影的样式是否为msoShadowStyleMixed。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Style</span> == msoShadowStyleMixed)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表中第一个形状阴影的样式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Style</span> = msoShadowStyleInnerShadow\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoShadowStyle",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Transparency",
      "summary": "<p>此属性的值仅影响均一颜色填充和线条的外观。对图案线条及渐变、图案、图片和纹理填充的外观无效。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定填充的透明度，取值范围为 0.0（不透明）到 1.0（清晰）之间。<strong>Double</strong>型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一张工作表上的第三个形状的阴影效果设置为半透明的红色。如果形状没有阴影，此示例将加上阴影效果。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Transparency</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第二个形状阴影的透明度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shadow = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shadow.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Transparency</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
